snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls Online: Deadlands Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The cataclysmic conclusion to the Gates of Oblivion year-long adventure begins! Explore a volatile, ever-changing realm of Oblivion and the bizarre city of Fargrave, gather mysterious new allies, and uncover Mehrunes Dagon’s ultimate plans for Tamriel. In The Elder Scrolls Online: Deadlands, it’s up to you to stop the Daedric Prince’s infernal schemes, 800 years before the events of The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion.

The Deadlands DLC is now available via ESO Plus membership or in the in-game Crown Store for PC/Mac and Stadia and arrives on Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation 4 and PlayStation 5 on November 16. It’s time to complete your Gates of Oblivion adventure and take the fight to the Prince of Destruction himself!

Official Site: https://www.elderscrollsonline.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/elderscrollsonline
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TESOnline
Instagram: https://instagram.com/elderscrollsonline

ESRB Rating: MATURE with Blood and Gore, Sexual Themes, Use of Alcohol, and Violence. Online interactions not rated by the ESRB.
